            </div>
            <div type="commentary" ana="b1">
                <p>"The monastery was built in two phases: initially as a hermitage by five Syrian
                    monks (ca. 420-430) - the period from which the oratory was probably built; and
                    secondly. as a coenobium during the time of John the Chozibite (ca. 480)."</p>
            </div>
